## рзлред PHP рж╢рзЗржЦрж╛рж░ ржкрж░рзЗ Laravel рж╢рзЗржЦрж╛рж░ ржЬржирзНржп Setup

**Laravel 11 (Most Beginner-Friendly & Job-Ready)**

* Official docs: [Laravel Docs](https://laravel.com/docs)
* Installation:

```bash
composer create-project laravel/laravel myProject
```

**Essential Laravel Packages:**

* Laravel Breeze / Jetstream (Authentication)
* Spatie packages (Roles & Permissions)
* Laravel Debugbar (Debugging)

**Folder Structure:**

* `app/` тЖТ Core application logic
* `routes/` тЖТ Web/API routing
* `resources/views/` тЖТ Blade templates
* `database/migrations/` тЖТ Database migrations

---

## рзмред Frontend Integration

* Tailwind CSS: [https://tailwindcss.com/docs](https://tailwindcss.com/docs)
* Vite (build tool): [https://vite.dev/guide/](https://vite.dev/guide/)
* Optional: React / Vue.js SPA integration

**Example:**

```bash
npm create vite@latest my-app
cd my-app
npm install
npm run dev
```

---

## рзнред API Development & Testing

* REST API: Laravel API routes + controllers
* Postman: [Postman Docs](https://learning.postman.com/docs/)
* Insomnia (ржЗржи-рж╕рзЛржо-ржирж┐ржпрж╝рж╛) (optional)
* API authentication: Laravel Passport / Sanctum

