## рзпред Deployment & Cloud

* Railway.app / Render.com тАУ Free Laravel hosting
* Vercel / Netlify тАУ Frontend hosting
* Cloudflare тАУ DNS + security
* PlanetScale / Supabase тАУ Free production-ready database

---

## рззрзжред Step-by-Step Learning Path (PHP тЖТ Laravel)

1. PHP basics: Variables, loops, arrays, OOP
2. Composer & packages: Install/manage dependencies
3. Laravel core: Routing, Controllers, Models, Views
4. Database & Migrations: MySQL/PostgreSQL, Eloquent ORM
5. Frontend: Tailwind CSS, optional React/Vue integration
6. API & Authentication: REST API + Postman testing
7. Testing & Debugging: PHPUnit/PestPHP + Debugbar
8. Deployment: Free hosting + domain setup

---

